         <li>
            <p>Press the AM or FM button repeatedly to select the band.</p>
            <p>
               <p>The previously chosen broadcasting station will be received.</p>
               <fig>
                  <image href="media/image430a.png" placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press and hold the AST button to automatically
                save receivable frequencies to Preset button.</p>
            <p>
               <p>"AST" is shown , and then stores stations in the order of their frequencies on the Preset buttons.</p>
               <p>Up to 6 stations can be stored in each of the AMA and FMA band</p>
            </p>
